== The Full 70 phonograms ==

The full 70 phonograms are:

a: ǎ(as in: cat), ā(as in: ate), ŏ    
b: b(as in: bead)    
c: k(as in: camera), s    
d: ď    
e: ě, ē    
f: f(as in:fat)    
g: g(as in: get), j(as in: gem)    
h: h(as in: hat)    
i: ǐ, ī
    
